  "description": {
    "de": "Eine schlecht sehende Féca-Seherin erschuf zufällig diese mächtige Waffe, indem sie bei einem unvorhergesehenen Sturz ihre Kristallkugel auf ihren Stock fallen ließ.",
    "en": "A short-sighted, grumbling, fortune telling, smelly old Feca accidentally created this powerful weapon when her staff rammed into her crystal ball as she slipped from the kitchen table. She'd read her own fortune long before and, well, she more or less lived on that table... Wonder what it was she thought was going to kill her... Well, I guess she wasn't the best fortune teller.",
    "es": "Una vieja feca invidente inventó por accidente esta poderosa arma cuando su bastón y su bola de cristal chocaron entre sí tras una caída que la vieja no supo predecir.",
    "fr": "Une vieille Féca voyante malvoyante inventa accidentellement cette puissante arme lorsqu'elle fit rencontrer son bâton et sa boule de cristal à l'occasion d'une chute qu'elle ne sut prévoir.",
    "id": "32466",
    "pt": "Uma velha vidente Feca com visão limitada  criou acidentalmente essa poderosa arma quando, ao cair, seu cajado colidiu com sua bola de cristal. Se ao menos ela tivesse previsto a queda..."
  },
